07:22.260 --> 07:22.520
Okay.

07:22.580 --> 07:25.820
Once the ink is dry and the property is handed over,

07:26.260 --> 07:32.200
the alternative futures where you didn't sell the house are legally permanently eliminated.

07:32.200 --> 07:37.380
Hold on. Let me make sure I'm really grasping this physical erasure concept.

07:37.580 --> 07:40.160
Because if the structure is totally gone,

07:40.520 --> 07:40.600
Yeah.

07:40.740 --> 07:45.400
It's like, imagine I give you a pile of diced onions on a cutting board.

07:45.740 --> 07:46.580
Okay. I'm with you.

