12:29.220 --> 12:29.680
broken.

12:29.680 --> 12:33.280
So we have to relocate the very concept of identity.

12:33.580 --> 12:36.900
We must relocate identity to the domain of the trace.

12:37.260 --> 12:43.140
Two things are identical, not because they share a past, or because they started in the

